longBusinessSummary: New Zealand Oil & Gas Limited engages in the exploration, evaluation, production, and appraisal of oil and gas properties in New Zealand, Australia, and internationally. It also develops, produces, and sells natural gas, liquefied petroleum gas, and condensate. The company was incorporated in 1981 and is headquartered in Wellington, New Zealand. New Zealand Oil & Gas Limited is a subsidiary of O.G.Oil & Gas (Singapore) Pte. Limited.
